00:24:41,179 --> 00:24:43,170
Not allowed to what?

259
00:24:43,248 --> 00:24:46,115
Huh?

260
00:24:46,184 --> 00:24:50,621
piggy! What? You didn't
see me, all right?

261
00:24:50,688 --> 00:24:54,886
And I didn't see you.
All right? Oops.

