And so, it was Christmas Eve.

300
00:29:39,844 --> 00:29:42,745
And time had run out for the pig.

301
00:29:42,813 --> 00:29:46,579
Are you doing him tonight then?
Mmm.

302
00:29:46,651 --> 00:29:50,678
Good.
The blood'll drain by morning.

