00:37:31,015 --> 00:37:35,179
We already have one, Mom.
That's the whole idea.

378
00:37:35,252 --> 00:37:37,880
We can send faxes to each other.

379
00:37:37,955 --> 00:37:40,890
Don't be afraid of it
just because it's new.

