01:10:28,089 --> 01:10:31,786
♪ If I had words ♪

705
01:10:31,860 --> 01:10:37,423
♪To make a day for you ♪

706
01:10:37,499 --> 01:10:41,868
♪ I'd sing you a morning ♪

